                    <h3>Introduction</h3>
                    <p>Cherry Hire, a sister concern of IPF HR Consulting, with its Head Office in India and Regional Office in Bahrain respects and protects the privacy of the users of the cherryhire.com website. This Privacy Policy is the basis on which the collection, usage ,maintenance and disclosure of user information is done by Cherry Hire.</p>
                    
