                    <p>&bull; The information provided by the userthrough the forms on the website www.cherryhire.com (Website). This includes information provided during registration on the website, subscribing to our services, posting job details or requesting further information or services from Cherry Hire. <br  />Some information may also be collected when you report a problem with the website.</p>
                    <p>&bull; If you are a Candidate, the information related to your employment history, skills and experience details that you have mentioned in the website.Also the profile photos and links to your social profiles and other publicly available information that are through a third party service.</p>
